snippet.title: Sanfu Release Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1880330/_/
For those of you who have been following:
Sanfu will be out on July 28, 2023. 
See you there on Sanfu, the Canicular days in China!
The story taken place in the mountain city is also the story of the times. The truth, is also the life of all.
